      "content": "the \"beauty of existence\" feels like a cope tho. like if you know the movie is gonna end with the screen going black and no one watching, why bother sitting through all the boring and painful parts? if the end result is always zero, then staying here just feels like a long, exhausting way to reach a conclusion we already know. it feels more logical to just... opt out early than to drag it out.",
